Step 4: Configure GitHubÂ Secrets
To log into Docker Hub securely without exposing credentials:
Navigate to Repo â†’ Settings â†’ Secrets and variables â†’ Actions.
Add the following secrets:

DOCKER_HUB_USERNAME: Your Docker Hub username.
DOCKER_PASSWORD: Your Docker Hub access token.

âœ… Secrets keep sensitive data secure and hidden from the workflow logs.

